{"tid":644181,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"華為代言人 Gal Gadot 用 iPhone 出post 撐 Mate 10","createTime":"2018-04-27T05:18:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-13T04:58:04.000Z","uid":1886,"like":84,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"5c8d85c25b509df219384cbbadb97dd069b0787d","tid":644181,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:18:47.000Z","msg":"點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://unwire.hk/?attachment_id=635689\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F%3Fattachment_id%3D635689&h=9dbc67b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"027814c7e90a26885457adad3f08ad817a1d9cdd","tid":644181,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:19:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4b48e95dff7af22765fa2246e41ba9037333a99","tid":644181,"uid":77569,"like":24,"dislike":23,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:20:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5c741f6ebc4e2a7b7c4f7588de11c37b473273d1","tid":644181,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:20:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a7c31fdb2d0ea2ff157b4f6de0c48396f3373b4","tid":644181,"uid":58413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:20:49.000Z","msg":"GG<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"992d36c62a9b67f285dc663160ef611104134ddf","tid":644181,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"明星名人為科技產品代言屢見不鮮，不過並非每一位都是科技達人，於是就出現不少「公關災難」。最近成為「災難」女主角的，正正是飾演「神奇女俠」的 Gal Gadot，她今年 1 月起成為支那手機品牌華為的品牌大使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，日前她就透過 Twitter 發帖為華為的 Mate 10 Pro 做宣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n可惜的是 Twitter 顯示貼文是由 iPhone 發出，網站 CNET 於是向 Gadot 的公關查詢，對方身為華為的品牌大使是否 iPhone 用戶。得到的回覆是 Gadot 非常喜歡她的華為 P20 和 Mate 10 Pro 手機。該尷尬的 Tweet 及後被刪除，並換上數個以 Android 手機發出的廣告宣傳，而 Gadot 解釋指她會請同事幫忙將較長的影片上傳，之前的 Tweet 正正是由一位使用 iPhone 的員工發出。<br />\n<br />\n來源：appleinsider<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/04/27/gal-gadot-use-iphone-promote-huawei/mobile-phone/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2Fgal-gadot-use-iphone-promote-huawei%2Fmobile-phone%2F&d=ZbLDp%2FSOqoVC0pFaSHQ%2Fr%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=b18199e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/04/27/gal-gadot-use-iphone-promote-huawei/mobile-phone/</a>"},{"pid":"91fc49461ac557f5224e77f7760e26e5d3c5721a","tid":644181,"uid":12628,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:30:24.000Z","msg":"碧咸同james 都係窮到要幫三叔打工咋，搵食唔易呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/133010_71b8a0d3e2735485a63d91f1fb428f9f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F133010_71b8a0d3e2735485a63d91f1fb428f9f.png&h=79b21c0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/27/133016_d491c231af76993ca625e67033cb84fd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F27%2F133016_d491c231af76993ca625e67033cb84fd.png&h=137c723e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"930ff5d760adf55e8fec7f844634f43412ec721f","tid":644181,"uid":76680,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:52:43.000Z","msg":"以為露點打格仔"},{"pid":"36bc475cfb4a058d3eb5a63dd2c9344baed90f8d","tid":644181,"uid":133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"992d36c62a9b67f285dc663160ef611104134ddf","tid":644181,"uid":1886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T05:20:56.000Z","msg":"明星名人為科技產品代言屢見不鮮，不過